&lt;p&gt;The Senior Content Author (SCA) is responsible for designing components and providing support to web applications. The SCA is able to work independently, assuming ownership for the design and authoring of simple and complex web sites. The SCA should also be able to provide estimates for their tasks and assume ownership for these estimates.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The SCA works with web applications and a variety of front-end technologies including HTML5, CSS and JavaScript, and is comfortable with content management systems.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You Will&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;_7e25325f _33487e32 _4f3c78e9&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Building web applications that follow the latest web standards and conforms with leading-edge front-end technologies, using the components implemented by the Development team&lt;/li&gt;
