&lt;p&gt;The Senior Creative Engineer leads and executes high-quality production design deliverables across digital platforms, ensuring efficiency, accuracy, and innovation. This role requires a strong ability to manage and deliver complex, multi-channel digital production projects independently, while also mentoring junior team members and contributing to the evolution of design systems, processes, and best practices.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The Senior Creative Engineer is a trusted partner for cross-functional teams and clients, providing guidance, quality assurance, and forward-thinking design solutions that align with brand guidelines and business goals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This position requires full on-site attendance, &lt;strong&gt;five days per week&lt;/strong&gt;, at the Barreal office (Heredia, Zona Franca Metropolitana).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;b7525896 c8f6b93b&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee the creation of production design deliverables in areas such as site/app maintenance, image processing, digital advertising, motion graphics, email production, and presentation design.&lt;/li&gt;
